summary:
I am a hardworking, passionate and highly motivated person for any kind of work I lay my hands on to. 

Working as a head waiter in the last couple of years has improved my English language to almost perfection, it gave me great organization and leading skills, so as my communication skills and that made me into a good sales person.
There was no dish that I couldn't present it on the best way possible or no problem that I couldn't fix, which makes me a perfect ambassodor for any kind of company in the sales industry. 
Spontanious and fast problem solvings are crucial in a fast-paced enviroment where time means money.

I am a constant knowledge seeker for the sake of self-improvement, especially in the fields of my work.
Adaptable, resourceful and open for any kind of job that offers a carrer.

For a glimpse of my life-style; kayaker, bike driver, recreational trainings, passionate guitar and chess player and many more.

Thank you for reading and if you have any questions please contact me.

Domagoj Nikić-Čakar
